      "updated": 1773612168335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PREROUTING (nat)  ->  can DNAT the packet before routing decides",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PREROUTING (nat)  ->  can DNAT the packet before routing decides",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ElwQg9qgvU6eRtiE3j0x5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 9068.739252088304,
      "y": -150.4389827286152,
      "width": 861.284423828125,
      "height": 18.75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#333",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1954482631,
      "version": 412,
      "versionNonce": 1903350215,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773612168335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FORWARD (filter)  ->  the firewall decision — ACCEPT means it passes through, DROP means it is silently killed here",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FORWARD (filter)  ->  the firewall decision — ACCEPT means it passes through, DROP means it is silently killed here",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "H8B04jAmxVuYi_krrJvmK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 9068.553822880382,
      "y": -113.13986447050684,
      "width": 1052.0843505859375,
      "height": 18.75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#333",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2007513319,
      "version": 410,
      "versionNonce": 853737703,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773612168335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "POSTROUTING (nat) ->  MASQUERADE / SNAT rewrites the source IP as the packet leaves (e.g. your router NATs your LAN to a public IP)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POSTROUTING (nat) ->  MASQUERADE / SNAT rewrites the source IP as the packet leaves (e.g. your router NATs your LAN to a public IP)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
